column4:
Purdue Pharma and the Sackler family fueled an opioid epidemic that’s cost Americans immeasurable pain and billions of dollars. 

@SenatorHassan and I want to make sure DOJ doesn’t repeat the mistake of letting them off the hook. 

Read our letter to Bill Barr: https://t.co/r7cJEAsuqU

Two months of ignoring the HEROES Act; 

Republicans still don’t know what they want; 

Republican Senators still divided; 

Trump a mess, tweeting and golfing; 

McConnell not even attending negotiations. 
https://t.co/XVB1N9MnA0

The Barr arguments are “preposterous”; 

the Barr assertions “pure misdirection”; 

the Barr excuse “reeks of pretext”; 

all to cover up “a gross abuse of prosecutorial power... to provide special treatment to a favored friend and political ally of the President.” https://t.co/4Cu5DquFJc
